          "reviewBody": "⚠️- This school is worst in Gurgaon don't consider this as a English medium private school it's like a third class government school, no one is able to speak & write good English , quality of teachers are very low except very few of them & even some teachers are very bad they hit the students very badly especially the senior teachers of classes  9, 10, 11 & 12 & primary wing teachers also , some senior classes teachers are mentally unstable & those psychopath teacher beats children to vent his anger those teachers need treatment from psychologist before teaching & i hope they left or management fired those worse teacher & some teachers have no ethics & behaviour also some teachers were partial & gender biased bcs. i faced some fake allegation by girl student which hurts me badly. This school have no extra curricular programs for social development of students, they don't organize any tech fest, sports tournament for district level & not even any fun school trips😔 in my time but don't know about the current scenario. The quality of the students are very bad they bully other students & fights a lot in boys washroom. This school also lost there reputation bcs. of some fight case within the management & daily fights outside the school, i lost my precious developing years in this 3rd class school, so guys pls. don't join this school otherwise you will destroy your future.\n\nThis school teacher needs education first in all aspects before teaching children!\n\nThanks.",
